<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About - Weather App</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      
      --text-light: #ffffff;
      --card-light: transparen;
      --primary: #007bff;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-light);
      color: var(--text-light);
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
      background-image: url('/assets/ChatGPT%20Image%20Apr%209,%202025,%2005_45_09%20PM%20(1).png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    body.dark {
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #1e1e2f;
      padding: 10px 95px;
      color: white;
     
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      width: 90%;
    }

    .navbar-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      max-width: 1600px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .navbar-menu {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .navbar-menu li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar-menu li a:hover {
      color: #00bcd4;
    }

    .logout-btn {
      background-color: #e53935;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white !important;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .logout-btn:hover {
      background-color: #c62828;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: var(--card-light);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    body.dark .container {
      background-color: var(--card-dark);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .toggle {
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      display: block;
      padding: 10px 60px;
      border: 2px solid var(--primary);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .toggle:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar-menu {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: flex-end;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-container">
      <div class="navbar-brand">My Dashboard</div>
      <ul class="navbar-menu">
        <li><a href="/dashboard">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq">FAQs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">Logout</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Our Weather App</h1>

    <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">My Weather Dashboard</span> ‚Äì your personal companion for real-time, accurate weather forecasts. Designed with simplicity and speed in mind, our app helps you stay informed about the weather wherever you go.</p>

    <p>Whether you're planning a weekend getaway, preparing for your daily commute, or just curious about the climate, our dashboard delivers <span class="highlight">hourly updates</span>, <span class="highlight">detailed conditions</span>, and a sleek, responsive interface that works on any device.</p>

    <p>üå¶Ô∏è From temperature and wind speed to humidity, cloud coverage, visibility, and pressure ‚Äì we offer a complete breakdown of the data you care about.</p>

    <p>We‚Äôve built this app using modern technologies like <span class="highlight">Node.js</span>, <span class="highlight">Express</span>, <span class="highlight">MongoDB</span>, and integrated it with the powerful <span class="highlight">WeatherAPI.com</span> for precise forecasts. The interface is designed to be elegant, responsive, and user-friendly with dark/light mode support and beautiful UI elements.</p>

    <p>We're committed to delivering <strong>reliable weather insights</strong> that help you plan better and live smarter. Thank you for choosing us!</p>

    <button class="toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()">Toggle Theme</button>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleTheme() {
      document.body.classList.toggle('dark');
      localStorage.setItem('theme', document.body.classList.contains('dark') ? 'dark' : 'light');
    }

    window.onload = () => {
      const saved = localStorage.getItem('theme');
      if (saved === 'dark') {
        document.body.classList.add('dark');
      }
    };
  </script>
</body>
</html>
